         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>Completed. This Ilakkaṇaccūṟāvaḷi is [dated] Jovian year Vicuvāvacu, month of Tai,
               17th day. Having begun writing on a Wednesday that falls on first [lunar day] and
               under [the constellation of] Aviṭṭam, it was completely copied by Aḻakappa
               Vupāttiyāyaṉ on a Wednesday that falls in the abovementioned month [i.e. Tai],
               twenty-fourth day, ninth [lunar day], [constellation of] Kārttikai.</p>
         </div>
